OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMoD pauses new Army housing
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fplans after backlash       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Ministry of Defence says it is     
OL,6, pausing its plans to change the        
OL,7, allocation of military housing after   
OL,8, strong criticism from Army families.   
OL,10,FUnder the plan, serving personnel would
OL,11,Fhave got subsidised housing based on   
OL,12,Ftheir need, such as how many children  
OL,13,Fthey have, rather than their rank.     
OL,15,FBut there had been significant         
OL,16,Fopposition to the move from officers,  
OL,17,Fwith a number threatening to quit.     
OL,19,FThe defence minister said the MoD      
OL,20,FU-turn came after listening to         
OL,21,Ffeedback.                              
